    serviceName: string,
    serverRole: string,
    host: string,
    port: string,
    transport: string,
    downstream?: Downstream
};
 
declare type StartTraceRequest = {
    serverRole: string,
    sampled: boolean,
    baggage: string,
    downstream: Downstream
};
 
declare type JoinTraceRequest = {
    serverRole: string,
    downstream?: Downstream
};
 
declare type ObservedSpan = {
    traceId: string,
    sampled: boolean,
    baggage: string
};

    span?: ObservedSpan,
